      <title>特朗普将指示官员加大对伊朗的经济压力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-04/trump-to-direct-officials-to-ramp-up-economic-pressure-on-iran</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，唐纳德·特朗普总统将发布一项旨在加大对伊朗经济压力的指令，以履行其前任总统所承诺的扭转宽松制裁执行制度的政策。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-04/trump-to-direct-officials-to-ramp-up-economic-pressure-on-iran</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Feb 2025 16:41:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
