    <item>
      <title>“这太离奇了”：特朗普冻结气候资金引发恐惧和困惑</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-04/-it-s-surreal-trump-s-freeze-on-climate-money-sows-fear-and-confusion</link>
      <description><![CDATA[自 1 月 27 日特朗普政府下令停止发放联邦补助金后，一些环保非营利组织和研究人员仍然无法获得补助金。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-04/-it-s-surreal-trump-s-freeze-on-climate-money-sows-fear-and-confusion</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Feb 2025 15:50:06 GMT</pubDate>
