    <item>
      <title>法官拒绝特朗普驳回资金冻结诉讼请求</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/judge-extends-block-of-trump-funding-freeze-plan-in-second-delay</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一名法官表示，特朗普政府“没有给出任何理由”在进行意识形态审查前不到 24 小时就切断可能高达数万亿美元的联邦拨款、贷款和其他财政援助。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/judge-extends-block-of-trump-funding-freeze-plan-in-second-delay</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Feb 2025 22:44:01 GMT</pubDate>
